<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span> صحيح - <span class="c2">((الروض النضير)</span>) <span class="c2">(١١٠٠)</span>: م. ⦗٢٤⦘<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
